                  "body": {
                    "type": "TextualBody",
                    "value": "<p rend=\"align(right)\">\n                                        <placeName>St Thomas</placeName>\n                                        <date>13 Jany 1852</date>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>My dear <addressee>Mr. Leeser</addressee></p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">I have not had a line from you<lb/> since\n                                                  <date>Aug</date> last nor has the Occident been\n                                        received<lb/> I am at a loss to account for your silence,\n                                        my<lb/> son <persName>Mr Danl Wolff</persName> who arrived\n                                        from <placeName>New York</placeName>\n                                        <add>?</add><lb/>\n                                        <add>?</add> the <date>10 Dec</date> informed me that he had\n                                        heard<lb/> of your being in health</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\"><persName>Dr. Danisch</persName> of\n                                                  <placeName>London</placeName> has translated\n                                        the<lb/> Pentateuch in English &amp; is continuing with the\n                                        entire<lb/> Bible I have a copy which is well done the cost\n                                        5/â€”if<lb/> you do not <add>?</add> yourself he will\n                                        supersede you</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(1)\">I have not heard from or of my son\n                                                  <persName>Elias</persName><lb/> since\n                                                  <date>May</date> last he was at that time in\n                                                  <placeName>Saltillo Mexico</placeName><lb/>\n                                        engaged at the Hibancan<add>?</add> Cotton factory perhaps\n                                        you<lb/> would be able to obtain some information of him\n                                        for<lb/> me, if so you would much oblige</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(3)\">With best regards I am yrs Truly</p>\n                              <p rend=\"indent(5)\">\n                                        <persName role=\"author\">A Wolff</persName>\n                              </p>\n                              <p>I have heard that <persName>Mr Carillon</persName> is dead &amp;\n                                        that he died<lb/> at <placeName>New Orleans</placeName> is\n                                        this so?</p>"
                  },
                  "target": "https://colenda.library.upenn.edu/items/ark:/81431/p3h41k680/canvas/p1"
                }
              ]
            }
